threescale.v3.api

Class ReportResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • threescale.v3.api.ReportResponse

  • public class ReportResponse
extends Object
    The response information from a Report operations. success is true if the report succeeded. success is false if it failed and the Error Code and Error Message fields will be populated.
